This paper focuses on scene text recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves the use of language statistics as top-down cues, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of energy minimization frameworks and deep learning approaches also suggests that this paper could belong to machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
